parameters.text:
=Task: Find 100 dental clinic website URLs in the United States.

Instructions:
1. Use Google Maps or publicly available online sources to identify dental clinics located in the USA.
2. Only include clinics that have a website listed. Skip clinics without websites.
3. Do not include clinics outside the USA.
4. Provide exact website URLs only, no extra information like addresses, phone numbers, or emails.
5. Return the output as a plain list, one URL per line, in JSON format if possible.
6. Make sure the URLs are live and correctly formatted (include https:// if applicable).
7. Limit the output to exactly 100 unique websites.
8. Exclude any websites already found in the Google Sheets tool.

options.systemMessage:
=You are an expert AI agent that finds website URLs of dental clinics located only in the USA using Google Maps or other public online sources.  

STRICT RULES:
- Only return valid URLs of dental clinics’ official websites along with the official name of the dental clinic as it appears on the website.
- Do not include addresses, phone numbers, emails, or non-dental businesses.  
- Always output strictly in JSON format with this structure:  

{ 
"websites": [ 
"https://www.exampleclinic1.com", 
"https://www.exampleclinic2.com", 
... 
 ] 
}


- Always use the tool `Get row(s) in sheet in Google Sheets` to check for existing URLs.  
  - Never return or search for any URLs already listed in the sheet.  
  - Only provide new, unique website URLs not found in the sheet.

				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-459fc523 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="459fc523" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In 1978, Navy veteran Dr. Glenn Ashmore opened the first Dental Depot office in Oklahoma City’s historic Linwood neighborhood as a small, family-owned private practice. Although that building burned down in 2001, during the construction of the second Oklahoma City Dental Depot location, community support helped us recover quickly. More than 45 years later, we’re proud to have just as many locations throughout Texas, Arizona, Missouri, and Oklahoma, with 25 here in the Sooner State alone!</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Dental Depot is a different kind of dental company. Even though we continue to grow, we always stay true to what Dr. Ashmore started—a commitment to delivering superior, compassionate, and accessible dental care with a friendly smile and at an affordable price.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Every Dental Depot is doctor-owned, which means our providers have the freedom and flexibility to provide you and your family with the care you truly need, not the services they need to meet a quota. We’re among the top three “Opportunity Oklahoma” employers with more than 545 people, and we believe in treating every single person—both patient and employee—with the utmost dignity and respect. Whether it’s educating our patients on their best treatment options or encouraging our team members to create their own futures, at Dental Depot, we do what’s right for the people we care for and serve, because it’s the right thing to do.</span></p>								</div>

				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-459fc523 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="459fc523" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">In 1978, Navy veteran Dr. Glenn Ashmore opened the first Dental Depot office in Oklahoma City’s historic Linwood neighborhood as a small, family-owned private practice. Although that building burned down in 2001, during the construction of the second Oklahoma City Dental Depot location, community support helped us recover quickly. More than 45 years later, we’re proud to have just as many locations throughout Texas, Arizona, Missouri, and Oklahoma, with 25 here in the Sooner State alone!</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Dental Depot is a different kind of dental company. Even though we continue to grow, we always stay true to what Dr. Ashmore started—a commitment to delivering superior, compassionate, and accessible dental care with a friendly smile and at an affordable price.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Every Dental Depot is doctor-owned, which means our providers have the freedom and flexibility to provide you and your family with the care you truly need, not the services they need to meet a quota. We’re among the top three “Opportunity Oklahoma” employers with more than 545 people, and we believe in treating every single person—both patient and employee—with the utmost dignity and respect. Whether it’s educating our patients on their best treatment options or encouraging our team members to create their own futures, at Dental Depot, we do what’s right for the people we care for and serve, because it’s the right thing to do.</span></p>								</div>
